General.Name: SHL Consolidated Bhd
General.Description: SHL Consolidated Bhd., an investment holding company, develops integrated commercial and residential properties in Malaysia. It quarries granite and manufactures aggregates; undertakes earthworks, building construction, and infrastructure works; and rents out plant and machineries. The company also owns and operates a golf resort; manufactures clay bricks and supplies finished brickworks of wall and other brick structures; provides professional construction management and geo-technical services; markets and distributes building materials; rents properties; and lends money. In addition, it provides professional management services in commercial and industrial studies; planning, construction management, and financial services; and strategic, financial, and corporate planning services, as well as operates as a marketing agent of bricks and building materials. SHL Consolidated Bhd. is based in Kuala Lumpur, Malaysia.
